          at all times. Bursts of compressed air are released through a super
          sonic nozzle, creating a pressure wave that rapidly expands each bag
          and dislodges the dust cake from its surface. The released particles
          fall into the hopper below, ensuring uninterrupted filtration and
          optimal bag performance.
        </p>
      </div>

